OL,3,C'We're local champions': Lib Dems
OL,4,Celection campaign launch in Birmingham
OL,6,FSir Ed Davey, the leader of the
OL,7,FLiberal Democrats, has launched his
OL,8,Fparty's local election manifesto in
OL,9,FBirmingham, during a rally with local
OL,10,Factivists.
OL,12,FHe described his party as a "credible
OL,13,Fforce" to run crisis-hit Birmingham
OL,14,FCity Council and other councils across
OL,15,Fthe Midlands.
OL,17,FThe party have 13 councillors in the
OL,18,Fcity, and said they're confident of
OL,19,Fincreasing that number.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
