OL,3,C'We're local champions': Lib Dems
OL,4,Celection campaign launch in Birmingham
OL,6,FSir Ed said Labour supporters are
OL,7,Fswitching their support to the Liberal
OL,8,FDemocrats, but he wouldn't be drawn on
OL,9,Fworking in a coalition if it was a
OL,10,Fhung vote on election night.
OL,12,F"Sorting out the bin strike"
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV News Central
OL,15,Fcorrespondent Mark Gough, Sir Ed said:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776017467
OL,3,C'We're local champions': Lib Dems
OL,4,Celection campaign launch in Birmingham
OL,6,F"Well, we really engaged in the
OL,7,Fcommunities where we rooted in
OL,8,Fcommunities. We're listening to
OL,9,Fcommunities and hearing their
OL,10,Fconcerns, whether it's on how badly
OL,11,FLabour has run this great city or the
OL,12,Fnational Labour failing, or things
OL,13,Flike the cost of living, which is a
OL,14,Fmassive issue.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776017467
OL,3,C'We're local champions': Lib Dems
OL,4,Celection campaign launch in Birmingham
OL,6,F"And so our manifesto, which we've
OL,7,Flaunched today with Birmingham City
OL,8,FLiberal Democrats, talks about sorting
OL,9,Fout the bin strike, for example,
OL,10,Fcleaning up our streets, repairing the
OL,11,Froads, dealing with crime and anti-
OL,12,Fsocial behaviour".
OL,14,F"The threat of Reform"
OL,16,FWhen asked how he would convince
OL,17,Fvoters that he is a credible force to
OL,18,Frun the city and run councils around
OL,19,Fthe West Midlands, he said:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776017467
OL,3,C'We're local champions': Lib Dems
OL,4,Celection campaign launch in Birmingham
OL,6,F"Well, our campaigning is doing that.
OL,7,FPeople are seeing across the city as
OL,8,Fthe one party taking on Labour. People
OL,9,Fwant to get rid of Labour. We're there
OL,10,Fand we're winning a lot of support
OL,11,Ffrom Labour.
OL,13,F"But there's something else happening
OL,14,Fin Birmingham. It's one of the reasons
OL,15,FI'm here today, to support the Liberal
OL,16,FDemocrat manifesto launch in
OL,17,FBirmingham. And that's the threat of
OL,18,FReform. There's a real danger that as
OL,19,Fthe Labour vote collapses here in
OL,20,FBirmingham, it can go to Reform".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
